article_title: UnitedHealth's Optum Targets 75 Markets For Health Center Expansion

article_metadata.description: UnitedHealth Group's Optum healthcare services unit is aggressively expanding into the healthcare delivery business, buying urgent care centers and expanding its role as a community-based provider of retail medical care
article_metadata.author: Bruce Japsen
